CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 15, 1963, p. 15, reads: "The 1963 Courier-WAMO Home-A-Rama. Pittsburgh's only home and food show, opened before a huge throng last Thursday, June 6, at the spacious Syria Mosque in Oakland...  6. HUFSTADER CADILLAC: In back - Bill Wright, Paul Dacey, Tony Farina and Ozzie Manuppelli. In front - Frank DeGrazia and Albert [Alberta] Thompson."
TitMainTitle: Alberta Thompson and Frank DeGrazia standing in front of Cadillac car, with Bill Wright, Paul Dacey, Tony Farina, and Ozzie Manuppelli standing in background, and sign for Hufstader Cadillac, at 1963 Pittsburgh Courier - WAMO, Home-A-Rama fair, Syria Mosque
